    <value>&lt;li&gt;Files you upload are stored in a temporary, session-specific directory on the server.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Temporary files are used only to perform the requested conversion and are &lt;strong&gt;never shared with third parties&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Temporary files are automatically purged after a maximum of 2 hours.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;You can initiate immediate deletion of your files at any time using the &lt;strong&gt;Delete My Files&lt;/strong&gt; button in the converter.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;We do not retain any copies of your uploaded or converted files after deletion.&lt;/li&gt;</value>
